  "growth_log": "v0.1 seeded from canonical P01 (SC-0006). v0.2 (2026-05-30): promoted P02's convergent vocabulary (41 values across proposition_kind/scene_kind/arc/tone/pace/communicative_function/high_risk_register_kind) via SC-0007 slots — see VOCABULARY_LOG.md. P02 now validates with zero convergent drift. v0.3 (2026-05-30): promoted P03's 27 convergent values via the CONFIRMED-only flow (default gate) — P03 now validates with zero convergent drift. v0.4 (2026-05-30): batch-promoted P04 (31), P05 (33), P06 (40) convergent values via the CONFIRMED-only flow — the full Ruth pilot corpus (P01–P06) now validates with zero convergent drift. v0.5 (2026-06-03, SC-0021): promoted 11 corpus-independent triage bares — tone RISING/STILLED/URGENT; pace BRISK/SLOWED/PAUSED/NARROWS/RISES/SETTLES/HOLDS/WIDENS — the locus-stripped/cleaned forms from the tone+pace triage (NARROW unified into NARROWS); tone/pace convergent drift across P01-P06 remains zero. See tripod_cleanup_log.md + SPEC_CHANGES.md. v0.6 (2026-06-04, SC-0022): promoted 56 reuse-dependent triage bares — 13 scene_kind (APPEAL/ARRIVAL/BLESSING/DEPARTURE/INITIATIVE/INSTRUCTION/LAMENT/MARRIAGE/MEAL/NARRATOR_INTRODUCTION/RATIFICATION/REPORT/VOW _SCENE), 27 proposition_kind (action-verbs + SPOKE + move-labels APPEAL/LAMENT/VOW/INSTRUCTION/RENAMING/BLESSING), 16 communicative_function_element (leading verbs) — the collapsed reusable types from the scene_kind/proposition_kind/communicative_function triage; convergent drift across P01-P06 returns to zero. See tripod_cleanup_log.md + SPEC_CHANGES.md. v0.7 (2026-06-04, SC-0022): added the role_in_scene_being axis — beings' participant role reclassified descriptive→convergent and seeded with the 21 ruled relations (kinship HUSBAND/WIFE/WIDOW/MOTHER_IN_LAW/SON/DAUGHTER_IN_LAW/KINSMAN/ANCESTOR/CLAN/REDEEMER_KIN/PEOPLE; DIVINE_AGENT; activity GLEANER/FIELD_OWNER/FOREMAN/HARVESTERS/FEMALE_WORKERS/MALE_WORKERS/TOWNSPEOPLE; referenced SOURCE_GROUP/ERA_REFERENT). The slot is now an enforced controlled relation set, not convention. See tripod_cleanup_log.md + SPEC_CHANGES.md. v0.8 (2026-06-04, SC-0022 deprecation): removed 133 orphaned superseded values no longer used by any pericope — 17 scene_kind + 54 proposition_kind + 40 communicative_function_element (the wordy forms collapsed by the triage) + 9 tone_element + 13 pace_element (the locus-stripped forms SC-0021 left behind, incl. NARROW unified into NARROWS). The old→new mapping is preserved in tripod_cleanup_log.md + git history; the registry is now exactly the cleaned canonical set, so reusing an old form drifts. See SPEC_CHANGES.md. v0.9 (2026-06-04, SC-0023): un-settled the 8 quarantined communicative_function_element used-once coin-flips (TRANSMITS/ANSWERS/PLACES/ANCHORS/INTRODUCES/POSITIONS/DISTRIBUTES/RECITES) — moved out of the approved set into the pinned quarantined-vocabulary.json. They were erroneously promoted as settled in SC-0022; they are NOT settled types. The validator now surfaces each use as a `quarantined` notice and a recurrence (≥2 pericopes) as an explicit RECURS in the corpus quarantine watch. comm-func approved set 16 → 8 (the recurring verbs). See SPEC_CHANGES.md SC-0023. v0.10 (2026-06-05, SC-0025): added the action axis — the nested component action slot reclassified from uncontrolled free-text to convergent bounded-open, seeded with the 31 SC-0024-cleaned verbs across P01-P06 (the 7 held sentence-shaped labels are quarantined, not approved — see quarantined-vocabulary.json). action convergent drift across P01-P06 is zero. See SPEC_CHANGES.md SC-0025. v0.11 (2026-06-12): promoted P08's 6 CONFIRMED values (scene_kind CONSENT_SCENE · role_in_scene_being PLANNER · arc_element REST_SEEKING_INITIATIVE/NIGHT_PLAN_INSTRUCTION/INITIATIVE_HANDOFF/TOTAL_CONSENT) from the SC-0063 drafter pilot, ruled by Marcia — the first machine-drafted promotion; see VOCABULARY_LOG.md.",
